===Etymology===
[[Category:Greek derivations]]
From Latinised Greek [[gubernatio]] "management, government", from [[Ancient Greek]] '''[[κυβερνισμός]]''', '''[[κυβέρνησις]]''' (''kybernismos'', ''kybernesis'') "steering, pilotage, guiding", from '''[[κυβερνάω]]''' (''kybernao'') "to steer, to drive, to guide, to act as a pilot".

